    "function has exactly 4 values here (hedging/connective/argument_verb/balance_and_conclusion) -- a first-pass taxonomy, not validated against a formal EAP phrase-function classification.",
    "This bank intentionally excludes topic-specific content -- if a phrase could be seen as leaning toward one topic (e.g. implying an economic argument), it was left out of Tier A and, where applicable, placed in Tier B instead."
